1
00:01:37,890 --> 00:01:41,030
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,060 --> 00:01:43,920
[Episode 5]

3
00:01:47,430 --> 00:01:48,509
Don't be angry.

4
00:01:48,509 --> 00:01:50,000
It's just a job.

5
00:01:50,310 --> 00:01:51,560
If Yuhua doesn't want you,

6
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:52,789
that's because of their poor judgment.

7
00:01:52,789 --> 00:01:54,250
It's not your fault at all.

8
00:01:54,759 --> 00:01:56,020
Don't blame yourself.

9
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:59,720
Stop being angry with yourself.

10
00:02:01,170 --> 00:02:01,900
Hang it here.

11
00:02:09,300 --> 00:02:10,250
What's this?

12
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,000
Well...

13
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,060
This... This is...

14
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:13,710
Well...

15
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:16,000
If I knew this would happen,

16
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,840
I shouldn't have forced you at that time.

17
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:18,590
Anyway,

18
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:21,120
I'm actually the one
who hurts myself and others.

19
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:21,560
Right?

20
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,360
I'm so contemptible, too.

21
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:23,690
Everything is my fault.

22
00:02:23,910 --> 00:02:24,870
I'll go back and figure out a way myself.

23
00:02:24,870 --> 00:02:25,440
Alright.

24
00:02:25,630 --> 00:02:26,360
Listen to me.

25
00:02:26,750 --> 00:02:27,870
Let me explain.

26
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:28,960
Regarding that outfit,

27
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:29,910
she left it here.

28
00:02:30,079 --> 00:02:33,210
I've been busy lately
and had no time to tidy up the place.

29
00:02:33,310 --> 00:02:34,000
Alright.

30
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:34,770
Don't be angry. Don't be angry.

31
00:02:34,770 --> 00:02:35,630
Don't be angry.

32
00:02:35,750 --> 00:02:37,680
See if there's anything
you don't like in the house.

33
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:38,510
Just throw them all away.

34
00:02:38,510 --> 00:02:39,090
Okay?

35
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:42,560
Stop crying.

36
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:43,560
Come on.

37
00:02:43,710 --> 00:02:44,820
Sit down.

38
00:02:44,910 --> 00:02:45,560
Alright.

39
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,520
Stop crying.

40
00:02:47,190 --> 00:02:48,850
I've never been fired before.

41
00:02:49,030 --> 00:02:50,760
It's just a job, isn't it?

42
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:52,030
So what if you got fired?

43
00:02:52,030 --> 00:02:52,800
At worst, you can just give up working,

44
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:54,710
and I'll support you financially.

45
00:02:54,710 --> 00:02:55,829
Do you mean

46
00:02:55,910 --> 00:02:56,630
I can stay at home

47
00:02:56,630 --> 00:02:58,560
to wash dishes, cook, clean the house

48
00:02:58,560 --> 00:03:00,020
and serve you like Xu Miyu?

49
00:03:00,630 --> 00:03:01,470
That's actually not what I mean.

50
00:03:01,470 --> 00:03:02,560
That's not what I mean.

51
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:03,820
Don't think like that.

52
00:03:04,910 --> 00:03:05,970
It's good if it's not like that.

53
00:03:05,970 --> 00:03:06,680
Let me tell you,

54
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:07,560
Nie Yucheng.

55
00:03:07,710 --> 00:03:08,510
If I marry you,

56
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,560
I don't want to be the second Xu Miyu.

57
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:11,840
I know. I understand.

58
00:03:13,190 --> 00:03:14,470
Do you think this is okay?

59
00:03:14,470 --> 00:03:16,360
I'll go to the travel agency tomorrow

60
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:18,560
to check
among all the hotels we're working with,

61
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,910
which one is better than Yuhua,

62
00:03:19,910 --> 00:03:21,770
and I'll select one for you. Okay?

63
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,970
So you're happy now?

64
00:03:26,190 --> 00:03:27,400
It looks like I'm doing the right thing.

65
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:28,030
Alright.

66
00:03:28,630 --> 00:03:29,790
Don't be angry.

67
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:32,800
You won't be pretty if you're angry.

68
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:33,660
Don't be angry.

69
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:34,700
Don't be angry.

70
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,560
Then what are you going to do

71
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:37,820
with Xu Miyu's things?

72
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:39,520
I'm going to throw them all away.

73
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:40,250
Is that okay?

74
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:42,750
Alright.

75
00:03:46,470 --> 00:03:47,910
I think in terms of hotel operations,

76
00:03:47,910 --> 00:03:50,290
we should not only
focus on Purong's brand concept,

77
00:03:50,290 --> 00:03:54,340
[Purong Hotel]

78
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:52,240
but also integrate this brand concept

79
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:54,170
into the daily lives of our guests.

80
00:03:54,470 --> 00:03:57,200
Purong represents a classic style of life

81
00:03:56,810 --> 00:04:04,110
[Purong Hotel]

82
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:59,079
and a kind of top-level dignity.

83
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:01,030
But the foundation of the hotel

84
00:04:01,150 --> 00:04:02,680
is still to serve the guests

85
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:04,800
and the people who live in this city.

86
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:07,070
Therefore, the important thing

87
00:04:07,090 --> 00:04:08,990
is to link with current trends

88
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:11,520
and promote the lifestyle
which Purong represents

89
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:13,230
to more guests.

90
00:04:13,870 --> 00:04:14,710
For example,

91
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,890
we can hold a street pop-up event

92
00:04:16,990 --> 00:04:18,680
with the theme of Purong's

93
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,370
classic afternoon tea

94
00:04:20,630 --> 00:04:23,060
so that Purong can enter people's lives

95
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:24,600
in a more accessible way.

96
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:37,930
Could you tell me if you've had
any experience in leading a team before?

97
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:41,980
Which hotel did you work for previously?

98
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,520
At...

99
00:04:46,070 --> 00:04:46,800
home.

100
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,190
Xu Miyu.

101
00:05:01,870 --> 00:05:03,070
Don't be frustrated.

102
00:05:03,430 --> 00:05:04,360
Work experience

103
00:05:05,070 --> 00:05:06,390
is just a prerequisite.

104
00:05:06,390 --> 00:05:07,190
It can't be helped.

105
00:05:07,190 --> 00:05:07,870
I know.

106
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:11,090
Actually, you're pretty good.

107
00:05:11,390 --> 00:05:13,000
You understand the underlying logic

108
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,390
and also have your own ideas.

109
00:05:14,390 --> 00:05:17,390
It's just that our hotel's threshold
has shut you out.

110
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:19,280
Thank you for acknowledging me.

111
00:05:20,060 --> 00:05:20,650
Wait!

112
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:24,160
If you really need a job desperately

113
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:26,270
and also want to
engage in the hotel industry,

114
00:05:26,270 --> 00:05:28,270
you may still have a chance for that.

115
00:05:30,270 --> 00:05:31,510
Starting from the entry-level jobs

116
00:05:30,390 --> 00:05:32,610
[Purong Hotel: We welcome you]

117
00:05:32,110 --> 00:05:33,560
seems like a detour,

118
00:05:32,610 --> 00:05:35,159
[HSKP Department]

119
00:05:34,159 --> 00:05:35,950
but actually,
it's to take it step by step,

120
00:05:35,190 --> 00:05:36,710
[F&B Department]

121
00:05:36,430 --> 00:05:38,210
which might be more down-to-earth.

122
00:05:38,210 --> 00:05:39,159
What's more, our hotel

123
00:05:39,159 --> 00:05:40,240
has exclusively established

124
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:42,560
a fast-track promotion channel
for our own employees.

125
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:43,680
Entry-level attendants

126
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:46,340
also have the opportunity
to become general managers.

127
00:05:46,340 --> 00:05:47,110
Thank you.

128
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:48,980
Think about it.

129
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:57,480
Hello?

130
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:58,990
I'm almost there.

131
00:05:59,190 --> 00:06:00,600
It'll take about

132
00:06:00,900 --> 00:06:01,780
20 minutes.

133
00:06:16,220 --> 00:06:17,160
Who are you?

134
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:19,530
You're going to break my door thoroughly.

135
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:22,160
What exactly is your relationship

136
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,720
with this little scoundrel surnamed Wu?

137
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:25,180
H-He's my landlord.

138
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,720
He's not your landlord!

139
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:29,480
I'm your real landlord.

140
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:31,600
He still owes me two months' rent.

141
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:32,270
That's impossible.

142
00:06:32,270 --> 00:06:34,730
I just paid him
half a year's rent yesterday.

143
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:37,700
I'll call him and ask about it.

144
00:06:40,340 --> 00:06:42,070
[Contacts]

145
00:06:42,370 --> 00:06:42,500
[Unknown Caller]

146
00:06:44,170 --> 00:06:45,310
[Unknown Caller]

147
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:47,800
Hello.

148
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:49,000
Is that Xu Miyu?

149
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:50,780
Yes, speaking.

150
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,750
Your installment loan
of 5,000 yuan for this month

151
00:06:52,750 --> 00:06:54,010
is about to be overdue.

152
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:55,720
If you still don't pay,

153
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:57,560
we will take extreme measures.

154
00:06:58,380 --> 00:06:59,390
I got it.

155
00:06:59,390 --> 00:07:00,600
I'll figure out a way.

156
00:07:09,270 --> 00:07:12,000
Ma'am, my bag is still inside.

157
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:14,500
We've received your report.

158
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:17,160
Go home and wait for our notice.

159
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:18,130
Officer,

160
00:07:18,270 --> 00:07:19,800
how long will I have to wait?

161
00:07:21,070 --> 00:07:22,230
I still don't know

162
00:07:22,510 --> 00:07:23,630
when the case can be solved.

163
00:07:23,630 --> 00:07:25,360
We will definitely do our best.

164
00:07:25,830 --> 00:07:26,920
This scoundrel surnamed Wu

165
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:29,240
took all my
and this young lady's money away.

166
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:31,390
He also stole many of her expensive bags.

167
00:07:31,390 --> 00:07:32,360
Officer,

168
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:34,920
you have to arrest
and punish the culprits for us.

169
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:35,920
Yes, yes, yes.

170
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,360
Please calm down.

171
00:07:37,650 --> 00:07:38,600
This is money,

172
00:07:38,630 --> 00:07:39,830
not orange peels.

173
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:39,870
[Reminder of Consumer Finance Repayment]

174
00:07:39,900 --> 00:07:41,080
[Dear Customer:
Tomorrow is your repayment date...]

175
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:41,980
Take notes of that.

176
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:44,300
Don't worry.

177
00:07:44,300 --> 00:07:46,830
We'll definitely handle it
properly for you.

178
00:07:58,790 --> 00:08:00,430
[Dad]

179
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:16,680
Dad, are you asleep?

180
00:08:14,730 --> 00:08:18,100
[Dad]

181
00:08:19,130 --> 00:08:19,340
[Mom: Inviting You to Voice Chat]

182
00:08:19,510 --> 00:08:20,030
[Mom]

183
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,680
Hello, Mom.

184
00:08:22,880 --> 00:08:23,770
Miyu.

185
00:08:24,430 --> 00:08:26,530
Why did you call us so late at night?

186
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:28,410
Your dad is already asleep.

187
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:33,200
It's about the loan for our guesthouse.

188
00:08:33,730 --> 00:08:36,080
There's still 5,000 yuan
to pay this month.

189
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:38,490
Can you ask Dad to transfer it to me
when he has time?

190
00:08:38,490 --> 00:08:39,240
Miyu.

191
00:08:39,750 --> 00:08:41,350
Did something happen to you?

192
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:43,659
Why are you asking your dad for money?

193
00:08:44,630 --> 00:08:47,060
Well, didn't we agree before?

194
00:08:47,150 --> 00:08:49,230
This money was borrowed under my name,

195
00:08:49,230 --> 00:08:50,790
but after the guesthouse was opened,

196
00:08:50,790 --> 00:08:52,550
we'd use its profits to repay the loan.

197
00:08:52,550 --> 00:08:53,990
Dad promised me.

198
00:08:54,020 --> 00:08:55,620
How come you're so tactless?

199
00:08:56,050 --> 00:08:58,190
Xu isn't your biological father.

200
00:08:58,330 --> 00:09:01,310
There are things
that he can't bring himself to say.

201
00:09:01,670 --> 00:09:03,150
Let me tell you the truth.

202
00:09:03,800 --> 00:09:05,660
Since the guesthouse was opened,

203
00:09:05,790 --> 00:09:08,150
only a few guests have come
in dribs and drabs.

204
00:09:08,150 --> 00:09:09,880
There has been no profit at all.

205
00:09:09,910 --> 00:09:12,360
Your dad has been so worried
these few days that he can't sleep well.

206
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:14,620
How would he have money to repay the loan?

207
00:09:15,500 --> 00:09:16,300
Let me ask you.

208
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:19,390
Did Nie Yucheng refuse to pay this money?

209
00:09:19,510 --> 00:09:21,510
Everything was fine two months ago.

210
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:24,240
Are you two still having conflicts?

211
00:09:24,670 --> 00:09:26,870
Couples don't hold grudges overnight.

212
00:09:26,910 --> 00:09:28,120
If that doesn't work,

213
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:29,440
I'll go talk to him.

214
00:09:29,870 --> 00:09:30,600
No.

215
00:09:31,270 --> 00:09:32,270
Don't overthink it.

216
00:09:32,270 --> 00:09:33,390
It's good if it's not like that.

217
00:09:33,390 --> 00:09:35,120
Just give him a chance

218
00:09:35,390 --> 00:09:36,790
to make up for his mistakes.

219
00:09:36,790 --> 00:09:39,050
Ask him to treat you better in the future.

220
00:09:40,390 --> 00:09:42,190
I'm doing this for your own good.

221
00:09:42,390 --> 00:09:45,630
You've been good-tempered
with a gentle personality since childhood.

222
00:09:45,630 --> 00:09:47,390
I'm afraid you'll suffer losses.

223
00:09:47,390 --> 00:09:48,630
Got it?

224
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,000
Rest early then.

225
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:54,080
I'm hanging up.

226
00:10:05,910 --> 00:10:07,720
Starting from the entry-level jobs

227
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:09,270
seems like a detour,

228
00:10:09,790 --> 00:10:12,030
but actually,
it's to take it step by step,

229
00:10:12,030 --> 00:10:13,390
which might be more down-to-earth.

230
00:10:13,390 --> 00:10:15,390
What's more,
our hotel has exclusively established

231
00:10:15,390 --> 00:10:17,680
a fast-track promotion channel
for our own employees.

232
00:10:17,680 --> 00:10:18,910
Entry-level attendants

233
00:10:18,910 --> 00:10:21,970
also have the opportunity
to become general managers.

234
00:10:35,970 --> 00:10:38,240
[Contacts]

235
00:10:38,370 --> 00:10:44,740
[Qiaoqi]

236
00:11:02,760 --> 00:11:03,240
Hello.

237
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:05,570
Are you hiring attendants right now?

238
00:11:05,830 --> 00:11:08,030
Yes, we are.
Have you ever worked as a cleaner before?

239
00:11:08,030 --> 00:11:08,830
No, I haven't.

240
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:10,840
But I've been a housewife for 10 years.

241
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:12,480
I'm very good at tidying up rooms.

242
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:14,440
What's more,
I've had an interview at Purong before.

243
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:16,320
The interviewer
recommended me to apply for this job.

244
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:16,850
Alright.

245
00:11:16,870 --> 00:11:18,050
Bring your ID card

246
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:21,750
and report for duty on the B2 floor
in the staff area during working hours.

247
00:11:21,750 --> 00:11:24,010
Do you provide meals and accommodation?

248
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:24,670
Yes, we do.

249
00:11:24,670 --> 00:11:25,410
We have dorms.

250
00:11:25,410 --> 00:11:27,000
Can I go today?

251
00:11:27,750 --> 00:11:28,480
Yes, you can.

252
00:11:29,670 --> 00:11:30,440
Okay.

253
00:11:30,630 --> 00:11:32,270
Then I'll report for duty today.

254
00:11:32,270 --> 00:11:32,670
Okay.

255
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:36,900
[Purong Hotel: Staff Entrance]

256
00:12:08,030 --> 00:12:09,550
Don't block the way at the entrance.

257
00:12:09,550 --> 00:12:10,450
Step aside!

258
00:12:13,920 --> 00:12:14,900
Come on! This way!

259
00:12:14,900 --> 00:12:15,900
Be careful!

260
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:17,140
Come on! Watch out!

261
00:12:17,150 --> 00:12:18,200
Come on! Let's go!

262
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:19,200
Make way, please!

263
00:12:19,200 --> 00:12:20,240
Come on! This way!

264
00:12:21,750 --> 00:12:22,670
Come on! Step aside!

265
00:12:22,670 --> 00:12:23,390
Hurry up!

266
00:12:34,870 --> 00:12:36,200
Are you a newcomer here?

267
00:12:38,510 --> 00:12:39,150
Yes.

268
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:40,400
My name's Xu Miyu.

269
00:12:42,840 --> 00:12:43,570
Come on. Follow me.

270
00:12:43,570 --> 00:12:45,430
The forewoman is waiting for you.

271
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:53,840
Ms. Zhang! Ms. Zhang!

272
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:56,440
Go ahead.

273
00:12:57,150 --> 00:13:00,150
The guest in Room 1821
wants to change to another room.

274
00:13:00,820 --> 00:13:02,260
It's that Black Card Ji again.

275
00:13:02,260 --> 00:13:03,990
Let him stay wherever he wants.

276
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:07,050
But we are short-handed right now.

277
00:13:08,870 --> 00:13:10,120
I'll ask someone to clean the room.

278
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:12,320
You guys should go handle the guest now.

279
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:14,440
Madam Cailu!

280
00:13:15,550 --> 00:13:16,480
Are you in there?

281
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:17,200
Who is it?

282
00:13:17,460 --> 00:13:18,460
It's me.

283
00:13:19,550 --> 00:13:21,080
Well, what are you doing here?

284
00:13:21,080 --> 00:13:23,080
I brought the newcomer here for you.

285
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:25,550
It's dusty here.

286
00:13:25,550 --> 00:13:26,680
Let's talk outside.

287
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:36,270
Let me introduce myself.

288
00:13:36,270 --> 00:13:37,390
My name's Zhang Cailu.

289
00:13:37,390 --> 00:13:39,720
I'm the forewoman of the executive floor.

290
00:13:41,150 --> 00:13:42,150
Hello, Ms. Zhang.

291
00:13:42,240 --> 00:13:43,270
I'm Xu Miyu.

292
00:13:44,030 --> 00:13:45,490
Your hands are quite soft.

293
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:48,340
You've never worked before, huh?

294
00:13:50,150 --> 00:13:51,510
I've done housework at home.

295
00:13:51,510 --> 00:13:53,200
You are 35 years old now.

296
00:13:54,910 --> 00:13:56,040
Age is not a problem.

297
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:56,980
Take your time.

298
00:13:57,870 --> 00:13:58,720
Yin Xiang.

299
00:13:58,720 --> 00:13:59,850
Where are you going?

300
00:14:01,510 --> 00:14:02,750
Take Miyu upstairs

301
00:14:03,090 --> 00:14:04,810
and clean Room 1821.

302
00:14:05,750 --> 00:14:07,150
Consider it as training.

303
00:14:08,750 --> 00:14:09,720
Don't you want the training allowance?

304
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:10,250
Yes, I do!

305
00:14:16,330 --> 00:14:17,640
This way. That room.

306
00:14:20,510 --> 00:14:21,570
The room at the end.

307
00:14:27,690 --> 00:14:29,090
Just leave the cart here.

308
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:36,630
Take the vacuum cleaner with you.

309
00:14:36,630 --> 00:14:37,260
The vacuum cleaner.

310
00:14:37,260 --> 00:14:37,720
Okay.

311
00:14:44,890 --> 00:14:47,030
Luckily,
it's not an extremely messy scene.

312
00:14:47,030 --> 00:14:48,030
Let me tell you.

313
00:14:48,030 --> 00:14:49,630
Opening a hotel room door

314
00:14:49,630 --> 00:14:50,890
is like opening a blind box.

315
00:14:50,890 --> 00:14:51,670
You'll never know

316
00:14:51,670 --> 00:14:53,510
what kind of mess the guests left inside.

317
00:14:53,510 --> 00:14:55,480
A couple of days ago, a woman came here

318
00:14:55,480 --> 00:14:58,110
and gorged on seafood and alcohol
in her room.

319
00:14:58,140 --> 00:14:58,840
You have no idea

320
00:14:58,840 --> 00:15:00,640
how messy she made the room look.

321
00:15:03,770 --> 00:15:04,690
Is that so?

322
00:15:17,480 --> 00:15:18,270
Mr. Ji,

323
00:15:18,400 --> 00:15:19,460
please have a rest.

324
00:15:20,270 --> 00:15:21,120
Thank you.

325
00:16:12,800 --> 00:16:15,750
[Shampoo]

326
00:16:22,050 --> 00:16:22,550
Hello.

327
00:16:22,570 --> 00:16:23,970
Hello. How can I help...

328
00:16:25,010 --> 00:16:26,810
I want to change to another room.

329
00:16:38,240 --> 00:16:39,490
Make this flush.

330
00:16:39,670 --> 00:16:40,350
Okay.

331
00:16:40,370 --> 00:16:41,370
Then fold it down.

332
00:16:45,690 --> 00:16:47,200
Fold this inside,

333
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:48,300
leaving a corner.

334
00:16:49,390 --> 00:16:50,030
Like this.

335
00:16:53,170 --> 00:16:54,430
Then lift this back up.

336
00:17:27,720 --> 00:17:28,510
Watch carefully.

337
00:17:28,349 --> 00:17:31,360
[Hairdryer Bag]

338
00:17:28,610 --> 00:17:29,540
The hairdryer,

339
00:17:30,640 --> 00:17:31,310
shower caps,

340
00:17:31,310 --> 00:17:32,030
nail files,

341
00:17:32,030 --> 00:17:32,770
hair ties,

342
00:17:33,400 --> 00:17:34,110
toothbrushes,

343
00:17:34,110 --> 00:17:34,750
combs

344
00:17:34,830 --> 00:17:36,360
and hand cream are all here.

345
00:17:36,440 --> 00:17:38,160
Soap. Remember all of this.

346
00:17:38,510 --> 00:17:39,400
If the left-and-right order

347
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:41,030
of these items in the drawer is wrong,

348
00:17:41,030 --> 00:17:42,160
you'll get scolded.

349
00:17:43,640 --> 00:17:44,810
Replenish two toothbrushes.

350
00:17:44,810 --> 00:17:45,420
Coming.

351
00:17:47,610 --> 00:17:48,410
One is enough.

352
00:17:52,530 --> 00:17:53,990
This hand cream is used up.

353
00:17:54,410 --> 00:17:56,140
Replenish a tube of handcream.

354
00:17:57,640 --> 00:17:58,360
Yin Xiang,

355
00:17:58,380 --> 00:18:00,330
clean up Room 1813.

356
00:18:01,270 --> 00:18:02,510
Why is there another room?

357
00:18:02,510 --> 00:18:04,030
Isn't Room 1813 empty?

358
00:18:04,030 --> 00:18:05,400
The guest in Room 1812 changed to it.

359
00:18:05,400 --> 00:18:06,550
Now he wants a change again.

360
00:18:06,550 --> 00:18:07,310
Copy that.

361
00:18:08,080 --> 00:18:08,960
This kind of guest

362
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:09,920
is the hardest to deal with.

363
00:18:09,920 --> 00:18:11,240
If you don't
meet their expectations even slightly,

364
00:18:11,240 --> 00:18:12,960
they will give you a bad review.

365
00:18:12,960 --> 00:18:13,590
Oh, by the way,

366
00:18:13,590 --> 00:18:14,750
you have to be careful from now on.

367
00:18:14,750 --> 00:18:17,070
Getting three bad reviews
means you will be fired.

368
00:18:17,070 --> 00:18:17,790
Let's go.

369
00:18:26,650 --> 00:18:28,100
Hello, room service.

370
00:18:38,120 --> 00:18:39,620
Hello, room service.

371
00:18:53,250 --> 00:18:54,450
Hello, room service.

372
00:19:06,680 --> 00:19:07,880
Hello, room service.

373
00:19:12,070 --> 00:19:15,550
It can't be helped. The guest complained,
so we have to clean it again.

374
00:19:15,550 --> 00:19:16,720
A bit further there... further back.

375
00:19:16,720 --> 00:19:17,760
Wipe the right side again.

376
00:19:17,760 --> 00:19:18,200
Here?

377
00:19:18,260 --> 00:19:19,120
The right. Yes.

378
00:19:20,830 --> 00:19:22,960
It's almost done. Clean the tea table.

379
00:19:41,830 --> 00:19:42,870
Yin Xiang! Yin Xiang!

380
00:19:42,870 --> 00:19:43,730
Let me tell you.

381
00:19:44,960 --> 00:19:46,810
He's so handsome. Super handsome.

382
00:19:46,810 --> 00:19:48,410
That incredible jawline.

383
00:19:48,510 --> 00:19:49,690
So handsome.

384
00:19:50,550 --> 00:19:51,310
A newcomer?

385
00:19:52,070 --> 00:19:52,930
My apprentice.

386
00:19:53,160 --> 00:19:54,660
Miyu, this is...

387
00:19:54,680 --> 00:19:55,370
Ke Wenxue.

388
00:19:55,680 --> 00:19:56,590
Hello, my name's Xu Miyu.

389
00:19:56,590 --> 00:19:57,350
Hello.

390
00:19:58,070 --> 00:19:59,960
How come I feel
you look a bit familiar to me?

391
00:19:59,960 --> 00:20:01,860
How come I feel I've seen you somewhere?

392
00:20:01,860 --> 00:20:02,880
Have we met before?

393
00:20:02,880 --> 00:20:04,680
Everyone looks familiar to you.

394
00:20:04,790 --> 00:20:06,200
Let's go. It's time to be off work.

395
00:20:06,200 --> 00:20:08,030
If we don't get off work now, the guest
might want to change rooms again later.

396
00:20:08,030 --> 00:20:08,560
This way.

397
00:20:11,270 --> 00:20:13,350
I just feel like I've seen her before.

398
00:20:26,150 --> 00:20:26,880
Miyu,

399
00:20:26,910 --> 00:20:28,250
this is your dorm.

400
00:20:29,200 --> 00:20:30,330
Remember this door.

401
00:20:31,090 --> 00:20:32,490
You can sleep on this bed.

402
00:20:34,230 --> 00:20:35,270
Thank you, Ms. Zhang.

403
00:20:35,270 --> 00:20:36,200
You're welcome.

404
00:20:36,270 --> 00:20:36,880
Rest early.

405
00:20:36,880 --> 00:20:37,810
I'm leaving now.

406
00:20:38,400 --> 00:20:38,880
Okay.

407
00:21:37,470 --> 00:21:38,530
It's true, huh?

408
00:21:38,960 --> 00:21:40,760
It really costs over 2,000 yuan.

409
00:21:41,550 --> 00:21:42,920
Well, if she's using
such an expensive suitcase,

410
00:21:42,920 --> 00:21:45,120
why is she working here as an attendant?

411
00:21:45,240 --> 00:21:46,640
Maybe she went bankrupt.

412
00:21:47,610 --> 00:21:50,270
Otherwise,
maybe she was dumped by her husband.

413
00:21:50,400 --> 00:21:52,380
Look. She's so much older than us.

414
00:21:52,410 --> 00:21:54,340
She must have been married before.

415
00:21:54,510 --> 00:21:56,990
Also look at her figure and temperament.

416
00:21:57,440 --> 00:21:59,720
When Yin Xiang walked with her
during the daytime today,

417
00:21:59,720 --> 00:22:01,760
she looked like a little maid.

418
00:22:01,790 --> 00:22:02,790
This is really crazy.

419
00:22:02,790 --> 00:22:06,520
Even the middle class is coming to
compete with us in this industry.

420
00:22:07,270 --> 00:22:07,950
Sit.

421
00:22:10,310 --> 00:22:12,920
♪ Face the wind ♪

422
00:22:13,480 --> 00:22:15,350
♪ Defeat the wind ♪

423
00:22:15,590 --> 00:22:16,370
Be quiet!

424
00:22:17,070 --> 00:22:20,790
♪ If time could be slower ♪

425
00:22:21,000 --> 00:22:24,000
-♪ I'll be closer to expectations ♪
-I'm taking listening tests.

426
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:25,590
Can you keep your voice down?

427
00:22:25,590 --> 00:22:27,030
Ms. Luo,

428
00:22:27,030 --> 00:22:29,350
this is a dorm, not a classroom.

429
00:22:29,350 --> 00:22:31,510
If you think this is noisy,
go to the study room.

430
00:22:31,510 --> 00:22:32,640
How ill-mannered.

431
00:22:45,710 --> 00:22:46,640
Although I was tired today,

432
00:22:46,640 --> 00:22:48,640
at least, I got to see a handsome guy.

433
00:22:48,900 --> 00:22:50,270
You enjoyed looking at the handsome guy

434
00:22:50,270 --> 00:22:52,000
while we were exhausted today.

435
00:22:52,550 --> 00:22:53,750
Keep your voice down.

436
00:22:56,000 --> 00:22:56,960
I remember now.

437
00:22:56,960 --> 00:22:58,030
The newcomer who came today

438
00:22:58,030 --> 00:23:00,440
was that rich woman
who ate and drank a lot

439
00:23:00,550 --> 00:23:02,260
alone in Room 1816 that day.

440
00:23:02,530 --> 00:23:03,960
Why did she come here?

441
00:24:01,240 --> 00:24:02,750
I couldn't have made a mistake.

442
00:24:02,750 --> 00:24:05,960
If there was a mistake, the receptionists
must have assigned them wrongly.

443
00:24:05,960 --> 00:24:06,590
Now that a mistake has been made,

444
00:24:06,590 --> 00:24:07,680
switch them back at once.

445
00:24:07,680 --> 00:24:09,030
I'm busy right now.

446
00:24:09,030 --> 00:24:10,240
I still have a pile
of guests' dry-cleaned clothes to fold.

447
00:24:10,240 --> 00:24:10,880
Miyu.

448
00:24:11,510 --> 00:24:12,790
You're here just in time.

449
00:24:12,790 --> 00:24:14,750
Yin Xiang
mixed up the takeout for two rooms.

450
00:24:14,750 --> 00:24:16,200
The lobby clerks mixed them up.

451
00:24:16,200 --> 00:24:16,930
Do me a favor.

452
00:24:17,030 --> 00:24:18,110
Make adjustments between the two sides.

453
00:24:18,110 --> 00:24:20,840
If the guests need anything,
try to satisfy them.

454
00:24:20,960 --> 00:24:22,290
Go fold the clothes now.

455
00:24:22,830 --> 00:24:23,960
Thank you both.

456
00:24:26,680 --> 00:24:27,880
Thanks for your help.

457
00:24:33,960 --> 00:24:35,140
I'm sorry, sir.

458
00:24:35,170 --> 00:24:36,310
We made a mistake just now.

459
00:24:36,310 --> 00:24:38,110
I'm here to switch your takeout.

460
00:24:39,030 --> 00:24:39,680
Okay.

461
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:42,030
Room service.

462
00:24:44,510 --> 00:24:45,070
I'm sorry, sir.

463
00:24:45,070 --> 00:24:47,930
-I'm here to switch your take-
-This is outrageous.

464
00:24:51,830 --> 00:24:53,960
How come it's you?

465
00:24:55,210 --> 00:24:57,020
You are...

466
00:25:22,070 --> 00:25:23,200
I sincerely apologize.

467
00:25:23,200 --> 00:25:24,820
This is our oversight.

468
00:25:24,920 --> 00:25:27,000
It was caused
by our staff's careless cleaning.

469
00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:28,790
We'll definitely deal with this seriously.

470
00:25:28,790 --> 00:25:29,510
However, regarding this matter,

471
00:25:29,510 --> 00:25:31,020
we've already investigated it thoroughly.

472
00:25:31,020 --> 00:25:33,530
It's entirely our hotel's responsibility,

473
00:25:33,800 --> 00:25:35,660
so you can rest assured, Mrs. Nie.

474
00:25:43,550 --> 00:25:44,310
Miyu,

475
00:25:44,420 --> 00:25:46,020
how is the adjustment going?

476
00:25:47,000 --> 00:25:47,750
I...

477
00:25:47,750 --> 00:25:48,480
I haven't...

478
00:25:48,500 --> 00:25:49,360
How about this?

479
00:25:49,550 --> 00:25:50,440
The guest in Room 1822

480
00:25:50,440 --> 00:25:52,290
has already ordered
at the Chinese restaurant.

481
00:25:52,290 --> 00:25:53,960
Now the key is that the guest in Room 1812

482
00:25:53,960 --> 00:25:55,690
is a bit difficult to deal with.

483
00:25:55,820 --> 00:25:56,990
I will go talk to him.

484
00:25:57,920 --> 00:25:58,780
I can handle it.

485
00:26:15,760 --> 00:26:17,740
[Do Not Disturb]

486
00:26:36,360 --> 00:26:38,850
Now that's all
for the takeout incident from last night.

487
00:26:38,850 --> 00:26:40,160
Luckily, the guests let it slide.

488
00:26:40,160 --> 00:26:41,220
Let's just move on.

489
00:26:41,720 --> 00:26:42,520
Luo Qingping,

490
00:26:42,680 --> 00:26:44,680
you are in charge of Room 1812 today.

491
00:26:45,240 --> 00:26:46,700
I'm not going to Room 1812.

492
00:26:47,080 --> 00:26:48,720
Are you afraid of getting a bad review?

493
00:26:48,720 --> 00:26:49,460
Aren't you afraid of that?

494
00:26:49,460 --> 00:26:50,550
If not, you can go.

495
00:26:50,680 --> 00:26:51,570
I've been there.

496
00:26:51,570 --> 00:26:52,770
We've all been there.

497
00:26:52,770 --> 00:26:53,600
You are the only one who hasn't.

498
00:26:53,600 --> 00:26:54,810
Alright.

499
00:26:54,830 --> 00:26:56,000
Stop arguing, everyone.

500
00:26:56,000 --> 00:26:57,200
Let's take turns.

501
00:26:57,440 --> 00:26:58,240
Luo Qingping,

502
00:26:58,380 --> 00:27:00,640
you're the most capable one on our floor.

503
00:27:00,720 --> 00:27:01,750
Go show him what you can do

504
00:27:01,750 --> 00:27:03,000
so that he can't find any fault with it.

505
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:05,160
Even the most capable person
shouldn't be treated like this, huh?

506
00:27:05,160 --> 00:27:07,350
Last time, I was also the one
who handled the weirdo

507
00:27:07,350 --> 00:27:08,350
who wanted his socks to be hand-washed.

508
00:27:08,350 --> 00:27:09,280
And before that,

509
00:27:09,480 --> 00:27:11,160
that family of five with three sons

510
00:27:11,160 --> 00:27:12,830
was served by me
from beginning to end, too.

511
00:27:12,830 --> 00:27:16,160
Madam Cailu, you just can't
cherish elites in this way, huh?

512
00:27:23,850 --> 00:27:24,450
I'll go.

513
00:27:31,790 --> 00:27:34,920
Hello, I'm the attendant
for the room cleaning service.

514
00:27:35,270 --> 00:27:37,200
Hello, I'm Xu Miyu
from the HSKP Department.

515
00:27:37,200 --> 00:27:38,720
I'm responsible
for cleaning your room today.

516
00:27:38,720 --> 00:27:39,880
May I come in?

517
00:27:40,720 --> 00:27:41,590
Yes.

518
00:28:12,750 --> 00:28:14,030
Are you going to stand here

519
00:28:14,030 --> 00:28:15,310
to supervise my work?

520
00:28:40,720 --> 00:28:41,590
Mr. Ji.

521
00:28:41,590 --> 00:28:43,990
Do you need me
to change the bedding for you?

522
00:28:44,940 --> 00:28:46,400
You can decide. Thank you.

523
00:28:52,070 --> 00:28:52,600
Alright.

524
00:28:53,020 --> 00:28:53,760
It's not necessary. Thanks.

525
00:28:53,760 --> 00:28:55,290
You don't need to change it.

526
00:28:55,970 --> 00:28:57,020
That's not okay.

527
00:28:58,160 --> 00:28:59,500
I have to help you

528
00:28:59,530 --> 00:29:00,790
change it thoroughly,

529
00:29:00,850 --> 00:29:02,140
from top to bottom,

530
00:29:02,170 --> 00:29:03,420
from left to right

531
00:29:03,440 --> 00:29:04,850
and from the inside to the outside.

532
00:29:04,850 --> 00:29:05,740
Otherwise,

533
00:29:05,950 --> 00:29:07,320
if the previous guest

534
00:29:07,440 --> 00:29:09,160
left something indecent here

535
00:29:09,180 --> 00:29:10,580
and you want to blame it on me,

536
00:29:10,580 --> 00:29:12,180
I won't be able to explain it.

537
00:29:27,660 --> 00:29:28,560
Mr. Ji,

538
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:30,640
are you always such a helpful man?

539
00:29:30,640 --> 00:29:31,830
Whenever you see someone in trouble,

540
00:29:31,830 --> 00:29:34,110
you just can't help lending a hand.

541
00:29:34,370 --> 00:29:36,200
Even if it means
covering up scandals for others,

542
00:29:36,200 --> 00:29:38,060
you still won't hesitate to do it.

543
00:29:38,600 --> 00:29:40,010
Why are you here,

544
00:29:40,560 --> 00:29:41,200
Mrs. Nie?

545
00:29:41,200 --> 00:29:42,200
Thanks to you,

546
00:29:42,790 --> 00:29:44,310
I am no longer Mrs. Nie now.

547
00:29:46,820 --> 00:29:47,560
I...

548
00:29:48,060 --> 00:29:51,260
I think there might be some
misunderstanding between us.

549
00:29:51,320 --> 00:29:52,980
Is there a misunderstanding?

550
00:29:54,200 --> 00:29:57,060
You helped my ex-husband
lie to me last time.

551
00:29:57,200 --> 00:29:59,200
Have you forgotten that so quickly?

552
00:30:00,590 --> 00:30:02,110
If my previous service

553
00:30:02,350 --> 00:30:04,160
caused you any unpleasant experience,

554
00:30:04,160 --> 00:30:06,920
I sincerely apologize to you.

555
00:30:08,800 --> 00:30:10,820
But if I'm not mistaken,

556
00:30:11,160 --> 00:30:12,690
it's your working time now.

557
00:30:13,030 --> 00:30:14,550
Do the attendants at Purong Hotel

558
00:30:14,550 --> 00:30:16,280
all like to chat while working?

559
00:30:21,280 --> 00:30:22,410
I need to take a call.

560
00:30:22,530 --> 00:30:24,330
Take your time to clean the room.

561
00:30:25,060 --> 00:30:25,870
Andrew.

562
00:30:26,480 --> 00:30:27,240
Yeah, sure.

563
00:30:27,240 --> 00:30:29,700
I'm not doing
anything important right now.

564
00:30:29,920 --> 00:30:30,670
Go ahead.

565
00:30:40,590 --> 00:30:41,080
Ms. Zhang,

566
00:30:41,080 --> 00:30:42,220
are you looking for me?

567
00:30:42,220 --> 00:30:43,220
Close the door.

568
00:30:43,380 --> 00:30:43,940
Okay.

569
00:30:51,110 --> 00:30:52,510
Let me ask you something.

570
00:30:52,510 --> 00:30:54,200
When you cleaned

571
00:30:54,200 --> 00:30:55,030
Room 1812,

572
00:30:55,030 --> 00:30:55,960
was the guest there?

573
00:30:55,960 --> 00:30:56,590
Yes.

574
00:30:56,590 --> 00:30:57,240
Did this guest

575
00:30:57,240 --> 00:30:58,960
pick on you to your face

576
00:30:58,960 --> 00:31:00,640
and deliberately
make things difficult for you?

577
00:31:00,640 --> 00:31:02,160
Tell me the details

578
00:31:02,160 --> 00:31:03,820
so that I can warn the other girls

579
00:31:03,820 --> 00:31:05,050
not to get in his way.

580
00:31:05,400 --> 00:31:06,480
He didn't make things difficult for me.

581
00:31:06,480 --> 00:31:07,750
He really didn't?

582
00:31:08,430 --> 00:31:09,360
You have no idea

583
00:31:09,380 --> 00:31:12,180
how badly Jia got scolded
when she came back that day.

584
00:31:12,180 --> 00:31:15,180
He said it was unprofessional for her
to wear perfume.

585
00:31:15,510 --> 00:31:17,640
Actually, the young girl
just loved being pretty,

586
00:31:17,640 --> 00:31:19,440
and her perfume was a bit strong.

587
00:31:19,850 --> 00:31:21,380
It was as if she had stabbed him
in the nose.

588
00:31:21,380 --> 00:31:23,240
Then he just gave her a bad review.

589
00:31:23,750 --> 00:31:24,680
Did he...

590
00:31:25,640 --> 00:31:27,160
also give me a bad review?

591
00:31:27,830 --> 00:31:29,510
He didn't give you a bad review.

592
00:31:29,510 --> 00:31:32,120
Encountering weird guests
like Black Card Ji,

593
00:31:32,140 --> 00:31:33,890
we attendants tend to suffer the most.

594
00:31:33,890 --> 00:31:35,950
But we can only endure the suffering.

595
00:31:35,960 --> 00:31:39,000
So we have to share information
with each other

596
00:31:39,030 --> 00:31:40,240
to avoid pitfalls.

597
00:31:40,240 --> 00:31:41,000
Got it?

598
00:31:41,240 --> 00:31:42,070
Got it.

599
00:31:44,790 --> 00:31:45,720
Ms. Zhang,

600
00:31:46,110 --> 00:31:48,880
why do you all call him Black Card Ji?

601
00:31:48,900 --> 00:31:50,030
You don't know this?

602
00:31:50,090 --> 00:31:52,880
Our hotel's top-tier VIP card

603
00:31:52,960 --> 00:31:54,590
is a black card made of graphite.

604
00:31:54,590 --> 00:31:56,250
There are only three in total.

605
00:31:57,000 --> 00:31:59,000
And that Mr. Ji has one.

606
00:32:00,550 --> 00:32:01,750
This person...

607
00:32:02,430 --> 00:32:03,440
is that powerful?

608
00:32:03,460 --> 00:32:04,540
This guy

609
00:32:04,570 --> 00:32:06,110
definitely has a strong background.

610
00:32:06,110 --> 00:32:07,870
He's holding a black card

611
00:32:07,900 --> 00:32:09,720
and staying on our executive floor.

612
00:32:09,720 --> 00:32:12,030
If he says someone is good or bad,

613
00:32:12,030 --> 00:32:14,160
his word carries much more weight
than that of the others.

614
00:32:14,160 --> 00:32:15,400
You must remember

615
00:32:15,440 --> 00:32:16,680
not to provoke him.

616
00:32:17,810 --> 00:32:18,350
Ms. Zhang,

617
00:32:18,350 --> 00:32:19,270
the guest in Room 1815

618
00:32:19,270 --> 00:32:20,600
is calling for service.

619
00:32:21,510 --> 00:32:22,350
Copy that.

620
00:32:22,350 --> 00:32:23,280
Coming right up.

621
00:32:23,590 --> 00:32:25,020
Go to Room 1815.

622
00:32:25,160 --> 00:32:25,680
Okay.

623
00:32:37,200 --> 00:32:38,400
Can't you see that?

624
00:32:38,580 --> 00:32:39,870
Pick them up now!

625
00:32:40,520 --> 00:32:41,090
Okay.

626
00:32:52,110 --> 00:32:54,370
I don't even know
if you guys understand.

627
00:33:03,920 --> 00:33:05,120
Come on. Here you are.

628
00:33:06,120 --> 00:33:08,190
Are they arranged in order?

629
00:33:13,510 --> 00:33:14,570
Are you a newcomer?

630
00:33:15,830 --> 00:33:16,960
What's your name?

631
00:33:17,430 --> 00:33:18,950
My name is Xu Miyu.

632
00:33:21,680 --> 00:33:22,200
Go away.

633
00:33:22,200 --> 00:33:23,130
Don't bother me.

634
00:33:24,590 --> 00:33:25,030
Okay.

635
00:33:38,350 --> 00:33:39,210
Miyu.

636
00:33:39,640 --> 00:33:40,640
You're not the only one
that's afraid of him.

637
00:33:40,640 --> 00:33:41,720
We're all afraid of him.

638
00:33:41,720 --> 00:33:42,790
I've heard

639
00:33:42,810 --> 00:33:44,040
that old man is a writer.

640
00:33:44,040 --> 00:33:45,110
When he's in a good mood,

641
00:33:45,110 --> 00:33:46,200
he acts like a normal person.

642
00:33:46,200 --> 00:33:48,220
But when he has writer's block,
he'll just scold others.

643
00:33:48,220 --> 00:33:48,790
Whoever has to deal with

644
00:33:48,790 --> 00:33:50,240
a guy like that is just unlucky.

645
00:33:50,240 --> 00:33:52,350
I actually think this kind of person
is easier to get along with.

646
00:33:52,350 --> 00:33:53,550
They don't give bad reviews
indiscriminately.

647
00:33:53,550 --> 00:33:54,830
They're much better than Black Card Ji.

648
00:33:54,830 --> 00:33:56,830
That's easy for you to say.

649
00:33:56,920 --> 00:33:58,180
Why didn't you go then?

650
00:33:58,750 --> 00:33:59,550
Ke Wenxue.

651
00:34:00,190 --> 00:34:02,590
Just put all this chattering energy
into your work performance.

652
00:34:02,590 --> 00:34:04,930
Aren't you just so envious of me
for having no bad reviews?

653
00:34:04,930 --> 00:34:06,240
Let's switch rooms and you can try it.

654
00:34:06,240 --> 00:34:07,300
Let's switch then.

655
00:34:07,300 --> 00:34:08,350
Stop arguing.

656
00:34:09,400 --> 00:34:11,699
Let's all try not to get any bad reviews.

657
00:34:11,850 --> 00:34:13,510
We don't need you
to be the peacemaker here.

658
00:34:13,510 --> 00:34:16,280
Except me, you're the only one here
who hasn't gotten a bad review.

659
00:34:16,280 --> 00:34:18,440
That's just because
you haven't been here for long.

660
00:34:18,440 --> 00:34:20,699
Let's see how much longer you can hang in.

661
00:34:23,670 --> 00:34:25,330
Room 1815 needs room service.

662
00:34:29,320 --> 00:34:30,980
Room 1815 needs room service.

663
00:34:34,500 --> 00:34:35,480
I'll help you clean up later.

664
00:34:35,480 --> 00:34:36,440
Just go now.

665
00:34:36,880 --> 00:34:37,510
Coming.

666
00:34:53,719 --> 00:34:55,780
Don't interrupt my train of thought.

667
00:35:05,000 --> 00:35:06,050
Engineering Department.

668
00:35:06,050 --> 00:35:07,310
Is anyone there now?

669
00:35:07,430 --> 00:35:09,420
The light in Room 1815 is broken.

670
00:35:09,480 --> 00:35:10,080
Copy that.

671
00:35:12,190 --> 00:35:13,960
Is it this late already?

672
00:35:14,590 --> 00:35:15,280
Xu Miyu.

673
00:35:16,210 --> 00:35:17,070
Come on.

674
00:35:17,090 --> 00:35:19,350
Come here and take a look at this passage.

675
00:35:20,130 --> 00:35:20,930
Come on.

676
00:35:22,590 --> 00:35:24,590
Look. What do you think of this part?

677
00:35:25,590 --> 00:35:26,450
[He put on that ring on the wedding day.]

678
00:35:26,470 --> 00:35:27,240
[The wedding was simple and plain,
with no grand ceremony.]

679
00:35:27,260 --> 00:35:28,370
[Nor were there any romantic vows.]

680
00:35:31,360 --> 00:35:32,420
It's well written.

681
00:35:33,630 --> 00:35:35,670
Does it show

682
00:35:35,670 --> 00:35:37,670
the hidden pain

683
00:35:37,670 --> 00:35:38,930
in Tingsheng's heart?

684
00:35:39,230 --> 00:35:41,320
Come on. Look at that ring.

685
00:35:41,360 --> 00:35:43,260
I added it on purpose.

686
00:35:41,430 --> 00:35:42,020
[He put on that ring on the wedding day.]

687
00:35:42,040 --> 00:35:42,610
[The wedding was simple and plain,
with no grand ceremony.]

688
00:35:42,640 --> 00:35:43,340
[Nor were there any romantic vows.]

689
00:35:43,760 --> 00:35:45,980
I just want to make it impossible

690
00:35:46,130 --> 00:35:47,330
to take off that ring.

691
00:35:47,710 --> 00:35:49,000
Since he can't take it off,

692
00:35:49,000 --> 00:35:50,510
he won't be able to resist

693
00:35:50,640 --> 00:35:51,760
that betrothal.

694
00:35:52,840 --> 00:35:53,970
Isn't it wonderful?

695
00:35:54,890 --> 00:35:55,650
Yes, it is.

696
00:35:56,110 --> 00:35:58,550
With your mention of that,
I've noticed it, too.

697
00:35:58,550 --> 00:35:59,710
Adding the ring as a prop

698
00:35:59,710 --> 00:36:01,630
is such a wonderful detail.

699
00:36:02,960 --> 00:36:04,380
If you can even notice that,

700
00:36:04,380 --> 00:36:05,320
the editor

701
00:36:05,480 --> 00:36:07,680
can't possibly say
he's unable to notice it, huh?

702
00:36:07,680 --> 00:36:09,400
They will definitely notice it.

703
00:36:09,400 --> 00:36:10,590
If they can't notice it,

704
00:36:10,590 --> 00:36:11,850
they must be blind.

705
00:36:14,350 --> 00:36:15,160
You can leave now.

706
00:36:15,160 --> 00:36:16,560
No need to clean the room.

707
00:36:16,890 --> 00:36:18,400
I'll stay here
to wait for the Engineering Department

708
00:36:18,400 --> 00:36:19,600
to repair this light.

709
00:36:19,760 --> 00:36:21,190
Just ignore it. You may go.

710
00:36:21,190 --> 00:36:22,880
Is the attendant-on-duty
of the executive floor there?

711
00:36:22,880 --> 00:36:24,030
Room 1803 is pressing for the supper.

712
00:36:24,030 --> 00:36:24,710
Copy that.

713
00:36:25,230 --> 00:36:25,800
Alright.

714
00:36:26,040 --> 00:36:27,030
Good night then.

715
00:36:36,040 --> 00:36:36,730
Thanks.

716
00:36:39,800 --> 00:36:40,730
You're welcome.

717
00:37:01,480 --> 00:37:04,140
Sir, did you enjoy your stay
these past few days?

718
00:37:05,280 --> 00:37:06,550
Please sign here.

719
00:37:08,780 --> 00:37:09,960
Could I take a minute of your time

720
00:37:09,960 --> 00:37:11,920
to write a review on our HSKP Department

721
00:37:11,920 --> 00:37:13,030
so that it can help our hotel improve?

722
00:37:13,030 --> 00:37:13,840
Sure.

723
00:37:19,320 --> 00:37:20,000
Hello.

724
00:37:20,710 --> 00:37:22,150
Have you finished reading it?

725
00:37:22,150 --> 00:37:23,190
This time,

726
00:37:23,190 --> 00:37:25,030
you have to pay me extra money

727
00:37:25,550 --> 00:37:26,710
for the costs of rush work

728
00:37:26,710 --> 00:37:28,400
and supper.

729
00:37:31,110 --> 00:37:31,880
Wait!

730
00:37:32,630 --> 00:37:33,630
What did you say?

731
00:37:33,880 --> 00:37:36,590
I wrote for you for over half a month,

732
00:37:36,920 --> 00:37:38,630
and you just quit with one word?

733
00:37:38,630 --> 00:37:39,590
Refund?

734
00:37:39,920 --> 00:37:42,320
In your dreams!

735
00:37:45,810 --> 00:37:47,860
Why are you standing there like a log?

736
00:37:47,860 --> 00:37:49,990
Do you think I'm such a laughingstock?

737
00:37:50,430 --> 00:37:51,460
I'm sorry, sir.

738
00:37:52,000 --> 00:37:53,300
There was nothing to eat.

739
00:37:52,150 --> 00:37:54,320
[Guest Satisfaction Survey]

740
00:37:53,800 --> 00:37:55,530
And no one repaired the broken light.

741
00:37:55,530 --> 00:37:57,860
How could there be such a five-star hotel?

742
00:37:58,150 --> 00:38:00,740
Take it to your boss, idiot!

743
00:38:12,820 --> 00:38:14,680
Ms. Zhang, are you looking for me?

744
00:38:14,730 --> 00:38:17,550
[Xu Miyu, 18th Floor,
Morning Shift, Bad Review]

745
00:38:18,470 --> 00:38:20,210
When did I get a bad review?

746
00:38:20,280 --> 00:38:22,250
It's all because of
that grumpy old man in Room 1815.

747
00:38:22,250 --> 00:38:23,630
He wrote some garbage

748
00:38:23,630 --> 00:38:24,670
and got his draft rejected,

749
00:38:24,670 --> 00:38:26,400
so he vented his anger all on us.

750
00:38:26,550 --> 00:38:29,150
He cursed the whole hotel
from top to bottom.

751
00:38:29,320 --> 00:38:30,720
We're really so unlucky.

752
00:38:32,320 --> 00:38:33,440
But this bad review

753
00:38:34,710 --> 00:38:36,230
isn't directed at me.

754
00:38:37,670 --> 00:38:38,660
Miyu,

755
00:38:38,920 --> 00:38:40,330
here's the thing.

756
00:38:40,590 --> 00:38:41,320
Come on.

757
00:38:41,360 --> 00:38:42,020
Take a look.

758
00:38:42,480 --> 00:38:43,630
She and she...

759
00:38:44,440 --> 00:38:46,340
Neither of them are good enough.

760
00:38:46,920 --> 00:38:48,980
They can barely protect themselves.

761
00:38:49,320 --> 00:38:50,980
So you'll have to take the hit.

762
00:38:52,400 --> 00:38:54,000
I have my difficulties, too.

763
00:38:54,070 --> 00:38:55,670
If I get two more bad reviews,

764
00:38:57,670 --> 00:38:58,740
I'll be done for.

765
00:38:58,790 --> 00:38:59,840
Don't be nervous.

766
00:38:59,870 --> 00:39:01,110
Let me tell you a secret.

767
00:39:01,110 --> 00:39:03,080
Even if you get three bad reviews,

768
00:39:03,190 --> 00:39:04,590
the hotel won't fire you.

769
00:39:05,440 --> 00:39:06,000
Really?

770
00:39:06,000 --> 00:39:07,960
They'll just deduct your bonuses at most.

771
00:39:07,960 --> 00:39:08,760
How much?

772
00:39:08,880 --> 00:39:09,940
All of it, for sure.

773
00:39:09,960 --> 00:39:11,560
You think he'd go easy on you?

774
00:39:13,440 --> 00:39:14,400
Don't worry.

775
00:39:14,550 --> 00:39:16,150
If you get another bad review,

776
00:39:16,150 --> 00:39:18,550
I'll also find someone
to remove it for you.

777
00:39:18,880 --> 00:39:20,340
Just do each other a favor.

778
00:39:25,280 --> 00:39:26,280
Okay.

779
00:39:33,500 --> 00:39:34,950
You need to eat more.

780
00:39:35,320 --> 00:39:37,160
Take good care of your health.

781
00:39:37,660 --> 00:39:40,760
[Longevity,
Happy Birthday to My Dear Mother]

782
00:39:38,070 --> 00:39:39,440
Wensi Tofu.
All the dishes have been served.

783
00:39:39,440 --> 00:39:40,770
Please enjoy your meal.

784
00:39:43,780 --> 00:39:46,750
[Longevity,
Happy Birthday to My Dear Mother]

785
00:39:43,840 --> 00:39:45,320
To celebrate this birthday today,

786
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:46,880
I'm really so happy.

787
00:39:47,480 --> 00:39:48,990
My son is successful in his career,

788
00:39:48,990 --> 00:39:51,510
and my daughter-in-law
even brought our family a grandson.

789
00:39:51,510 --> 00:39:53,110
I am completely content.

790
00:39:53,110 --> 00:39:54,070
Thank you all.

791
00:39:53,190 --> 00:39:57,150
[Longevity,
Happy Birthday to My Dear Mother]

792
00:39:55,320 --> 00:39:56,400
Mom, happy birthday.

793
00:39:56,400 --> 00:39:56,980
Cheers.

794
00:39:57,230 --> 00:39:59,090
-Happy birthday.
-Happy birthday.

795
00:39:59,090 --> 00:39:59,480
Thank you.

796
00:39:59,480 --> 00:40:00,790
I wish you good health.

797
00:40:00,920 --> 00:40:02,550
Thank you.

798
00:40:02,590 --> 00:40:04,220
How come Mom knows it's a boy?

799
00:40:06,940 --> 00:40:08,140
Everyone, let's eat.

800
00:40:08,460 --> 00:40:09,760
Please help yourselves.

801
00:40:09,760 --> 00:40:10,840
This Purong Hotel

802
00:40:10,840 --> 00:40:12,300
is indeed magnificent.

803
00:40:12,590 --> 00:40:15,050
I've always wanted to come in
and take a look.

804
00:40:15,150 --> 00:40:15,840
Thanks to you,

805
00:40:15,840 --> 00:40:17,750
I can do so today.

806
00:40:17,770 --> 00:40:18,730
Not at all.

807
00:40:19,000 --> 00:40:21,800
This is just a small gesture
from the younger ones.

808
00:40:23,110 --> 00:40:23,880
Mr. Nie.

809
00:40:24,280 --> 00:40:24,920
Mr. Wei.

810
00:40:25,030 --> 00:40:26,230
Welcome to our hotel.

811
00:40:26,400 --> 00:40:27,110
It's very nice of you to say that.

812
00:40:27,110 --> 00:40:27,920
Thank you.

813
00:40:27,960 --> 00:40:29,000
This room is well decorated.

814
00:40:29,000 --> 00:40:30,460
Thanks for your hard work.

815
00:40:30,880 --> 00:40:32,110
Let me make an introduction.

816
00:40:32,110 --> 00:40:33,910
This is the head of Purong Hotel,

817
00:40:33,950 --> 00:40:34,990
Mr. Wei Siyuan.

818
00:40:35,020 --> 00:40:36,030
Don't call me the head.

819
00:40:36,030 --> 00:40:36,800
I'm just the chief butler,

820
00:40:36,800 --> 00:40:37,880
aiming at serving everyone.

821
00:40:37,880 --> 00:40:38,840
What chief butler?

822
00:40:38,840 --> 00:40:40,040
You are just the head.

823
00:40:40,760 --> 00:40:41,440
Mr. Wei,

824
00:40:41,440 --> 00:40:42,370
nice to meet you.

825
00:40:42,630 --> 00:40:43,620
This is my mother.

826
00:40:43,620 --> 00:40:44,870
You can call me Wei.

827
00:40:45,480 --> 00:40:46,190
Mrs. Nie,

828
00:40:46,280 --> 00:40:47,030
today, it's my great honor

829
00:40:47,030 --> 00:40:48,360
that you can celebrate your birthday

830
00:40:48,360 --> 00:40:49,670
in our hotel.

831
00:40:49,710 --> 00:40:50,800
I have to drink a toast to you properly.

832
00:40:50,800 --> 00:40:51,190
Thank you.

833
00:40:51,190 --> 00:40:52,280
-Thank you, Mr. Wei.
-May you...

834
00:40:52,280 --> 00:40:54,310
Remain happy every day just like today,

835
00:40:54,310 --> 00:40:56,560
and stay young forever.

836
00:40:57,840 --> 00:40:59,340
Mr. Wei, it's very kind of you
to say that.

837
00:40:59,340 --> 00:41:00,190
Please drink as you prefer.

838
00:41:00,190 --> 00:41:00,870
Okay.

839
00:41:01,190 --> 00:41:01,990
Have a seat.

840
00:41:02,010 --> 00:41:03,410
Come on. Refill my glass.

841
00:41:04,150 --> 00:41:05,030
Come on, Mr. Nie.

842
00:41:05,030 --> 00:41:05,800
Come on.

843
00:41:05,800 --> 00:41:06,550
Let me drink a toast to you individually.

844
00:41:06,550 --> 00:41:07,360
Come on.

845
00:41:07,800 --> 00:41:08,480
Thank you.

846
00:41:08,480 --> 00:41:09,550
Mr. Nie here

847
00:41:09,550 --> 00:41:10,710
is a true winner in life.

848
00:41:10,710 --> 00:41:11,670
He really deserves this reputation.

849
00:41:11,670 --> 00:41:12,880
Thanks for your kind words.

850
00:41:12,880 --> 00:41:14,540
Let's move forward together.

851
00:41:14,800 --> 00:41:15,440
Let's move forward together.

852
00:41:15,440 --> 00:41:16,280
Cheers.

853
00:41:18,710 --> 00:41:20,280
Alright. Since this is a family feast,

854
00:41:20,280 --> 00:41:22,000
I won't disturb you any longer.

855
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:22,630
Please forgive us

856
00:41:22,630 --> 00:41:23,920
if there's any oversight in our service.

857
00:41:23,920 --> 00:41:25,410
Kaixin,
stay here and take good care of them.

858
00:41:25,410 --> 00:41:25,760
Okay.

859
00:41:25,760 --> 00:41:26,760
Please enjoy your meal.

860
00:41:26,760 --> 00:41:27,690
I'm leaving now.

861
00:41:28,400 --> 00:41:29,600
Mom, I'll see him out.

862
00:41:30,840 --> 00:41:31,670
Mr. Wei.

863
00:41:33,070 --> 00:41:33,900
Here's the thing.

864
00:41:33,900 --> 00:41:35,400
From now on,

865
00:41:35,400 --> 00:41:37,600
