996
00:44:49,280 --> 00:44:50,360
Not at all.

997
00:44:50,590 --> 00:44:51,760
Alright. Let's eat.

998
00:44:51,760 --> 00:44:52,820
Come on. Let's eat.

999
00:44:55,320 --> 00:44:57,510
Ask the attendant-on-duty
of the executive floor to come here now.

1000
00:44:57,510 --> 00:44:58,000
Hurry up!

